          <title>Sen. Mitch McConnell won't seek reelection in 2026, ending long tenure as Republican power broker</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Fellow senators have clapped for Mitch McConnell after he announced he won’t seek reelection next year. The Kentucky Republican is ending a decadeslong tenure as a power broker who championed conservative causes but ultimately ceded ground to the fierce populism of President Donald Trump.]]></description>
